section.para:
To enable PostgreSQL, add the following to your configuration.nix:
= true; = pkgs.postgresql_9_4;
Note that you are required to specify the desired version of PostgreSQL (e.g. pkgs.postgresql_9_4). Since upgrading your PostgreSQL version requires a database dump and reload (see below), NixOS cannot provide a default value for such as the most recent release of PostgreSQL.
